<h2>Data Attribution</h2>

<h3>Transport Data</h3>
<p>Real-time and schedule transit data is sourced from the <strong>National Transport Authority of Ireland (NTA)</strong> via the GTFS-R feed. &copy; NTA. Use of this data is subject to NTA's open data licence.</p>

<h3>Energy Data</h3>
<p>Electricity grid data is sourced from <strong>EirGrid plc</strong> via the Smart Grid Dashboard API. &copy; EirGrid plc. EirGrid is the operator of the Irish national electricity transmission system.</p>

<h3>Maps</h3>
<p>Maps and location services are powered by <strong>Google Maps</strong>, &copy; Google. Use of Google Maps is subject to Google's Terms of Service and Privacy Policy.</p>

